{"tid":903844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"取消香港關系法日誌推演!","createTime":"2018-11-16T01:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T10:08:22.000Z","uid":53577,"like":16,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1f769efde3db965c9154c8fd17b51f906f26c954","tid":903844,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"day1 星期六 <br />\n<br />\n收到消息後街上一片死寂，全部人喱埋屋企上網訂機票，準備短期内離開香港，有啲人係怕暴動，有啲人係覺得好政治呀要散下心先，有啲早準備好嘅直頭say gooodbye(包括淋鄭同建制派啲屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n旁晚已出現人龍喺各銀行排隊，準備兩日後開門擠提(換美金?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太天真了）"},{"pid":"4690b843db2ccaf6245704a7f0b00870d82d8435","tid":903844,"uid":53577,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:42:48.000Z","msg":"day2 sunday<br />\n<br />\n早上8點鐘，淋病上cctvb緊急新聞發佈會，表示對美國做法非常遺憾，決定委托曾俊華向美國解釋香港特殊地位，另傳聞時任財政司陳茂皮已出逃英國!<br />\n<br />\n中午1200時，解放軍車進駐各大學及社區會堂停車場，準備行動.<br />\n<br />\n致下午2時，各銀行門口，已聚集恐佈人龍，排隊排到狗鐵各車站，擠提市民連車都唔使落，直接可以馬上排隊!"},{"pid":"1e626590c6219a4358f575f03500d283d8d930f7","tid":903844,"uid":216664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"支爆了"},{"pid":"d617ebedc94236c112520da1cda98b4e36db3b17","tid":903844,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c240fd2012521f13818d7aa58e3f15d4f1d7610","tid":903844,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:48:28.000Z","msg":"繼續星期日晚上, cctvb報導星期一全港停工一天，係香港開埠以嚟全部香港人第一次唔使返工!"},{"pid":"63a8f35d11d6d6e5c4568af503c1c5731c9b5459","tid":903844,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:50:19.000Z","msg":"香港人無糧出都要返工喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9a7f453d62ee469a316a8434e8a13692e235af","tid":903844,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63a8f35d11d6d6e5c4568af503c1c5731c9b5459","tid":903844,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:50:19.000Z","msg":"香港人無糧出都要返工喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"話咗停工，連看更都唔返工冇人開門比你"},{"pid":"ef35f0380cf00fbc2a5a3f522ac1a490a19894ad","tid":903844,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">連你都冇糧出呀五毛樓主<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pC2sW7i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpC2sW7i.png&h=83e5e535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"bf89da3c3626d0f69d6c7234614ff38449b8a5d7","tid":903844,"uid":53577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:58:53.000Z","msg":"繼續星期日 晚上， 各區大量出現暴力搶刧強姦，人心惶惶，除咗排隊擠提人龍，冇人敢出街， 講漏咗，早上發生市民去超市搶掠物資屯積粮水， 食物供應已收皮."},{"pid":"614866dc425f4f78e208816148f6fa52a184c481","tid":903844,"uid":53577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"繼續星期日 晚上，淋病宣佈，介於現時社會出現莫名其妙嘅亂像，政苦宣佈，香港星期一零晨時起戒嚴! 銀行排隊市民要立即返屋企，並宣佈香港停工致星期三返工!<br />\n<br />\n解放軍進入各區部署，並在95式槍上罕有哋裝上刺刀."},{"pid":"d42eda61470aa283cdfedfcfef088516ea3fd4f6","tid":903844,"uid":140588,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"星期一，美國採取進一步行動並公佈中國大陸所有官員在美資產名單！ 中國各地所有群眾譁然！并開始有零星嘅衝突， 同要求習近平下台，解放軍出動鎮壓， 而美國以保護在香港資產及所有美籍人員的安全為由！ 下令太平洋航空母艦戰鬥群駛入香港......"},{"pid":"6bbdf91a1298da08db2ddb0716eea22a04577a61","tid":903844,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef35f0380cf00fbc2a5a3f522ac1a490a19894ad","tid":903844,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">連你都冇糧出呀五毛樓主<br />\n<img src=\"htt